data.description: Seller adjusted the price again. Back on the market again. Buyer could not approve for loan. All paperwork is completed. Buyer could be in by Christmas.    Seller anxious. Large Price Improvement and worth a trip. Beautifully maintained home by this owner. Updated appliances, bronze fixtures in bathrooms, fresh paint throughout, some ship lap wall coverings, window coverings, crown molding, and ceiling fans. Garage comes with ship lap walls, floored attic in garage, covered patio, and sprinkler system. Great location with highway near for perfect commute. Compare the square footage to others. Seller has a survey and T-47.
